            "description": "Create a new experience entry (project, job, internship, or volunteering).\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `title` (required): Title of the experience\n- `summary` (optional): Description of the experience\n- `start` (optional): Start date in ISO 8601 format\n- `end` (optional): End date in ISO 8601 format\n- `kind` (optional): Type of experience - one of: `internship`, `project`, `job`, `volunteering`"
